==English==
===Etymology===

The term is used as a sub category of '[[childlover]]'. [[Pedophiles]] and 'Pedophile' / 'Youth liberation' advocates created this set of definitions, as 'Pedophile' has become a false [[synonym]] for an often [[sadistic]] child abuser.

===Noun===
'''girllover'''
#A female-oriented non-[[sadistic]] [[pedophile]].

